Resource Profile: 病人資訊-Patient TWPAS

Official URL: https://nhicore.nhi.gov.tw/pas/StructureDefinition/Patient-twpas Version: 1.0.6
Active as of 2025-07-30 Computable Name: PatientTWPAS

此病人資訊-Patient TWPAS Profile說明本IG如何進一步定義臺灣核心-病人(TW Core Patient) Profile以呈現癌藥事前審查之病人基本資料

Usages:

  • Use this Profile: 事前審查-Bundle TWPAS
  • Refer to this Profile: 事前審查-Claim TWPAS, 自主審查報備-ClaimResponse Self Assessment TWPAS, 事前審查回覆-ClaimResponse TWPAS, 健保事前審查計畫-Coverage TWPAS... Show 15 more, 影像報告-DiagnosticReport Image TWPAS, 檢查報告-DiagnosticReport TWPAS, 文件參照-DocumentReference TWPAS, 就醫科別-Encounter TWPAS, DICOM影像-ImagingStudy TWPAS, 非DICOM影像-Media TWPAS, 事前審查品項-MedicationRequest Apply TWPAS, 用藥品項-MedicationRequest Treat TWPAS, 癌症分期量表-Observation Cancer Stage TWPAS, 基因資訊-Observation Diagnostic TWPAS, 檢驗檢查-Observation Laboratory Result TWPAS, 病人狀態評估-Observation Patient Assessment TWPAS, 治療後疾病狀態評估-Observation Treatment Assessment TWPAS, 放射治療-Procedure TWPAS and 基因檢測檢體-Specimen TWPAS
  • Examples for this Profile: Patient/pat-min
  • CapabilityStatements using this Profile: 臺灣癌藥事前審查-用戶端(TWPAS Client) and 臺灣癌藥事前審查-伺服端(TWPAS Server)

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
